Interface PriorityQueues<E>

All Known Implementing Classes:
PriQueHeap, PriQueHeapComparator
public interface PriorityQueues<E>

PriorityQueue interface for priority queues for all kind of elements implementing Comparable. The highest priority has the element which is smallest according to the method compareTo in Comparable or according to a given Comparator.

Version:
(2007)
Author:
(Bror Bjerner)
